WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:02.050
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.050 --> 00:00:05.050
I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:05.319 --> 00:00:07.926
Seriously, this is an exciting time.

00:00:07.926 --> 00:00:18.346
We are making headway in the spirit realm, praying over the elections and the attacks that I've seen coming—things the Lord is warning me about.

00:00:18.719 --> 00:00:28.248
I have to be careful what I say on this platform because YouTube censors things, so I have to flow with what I feel I can say.

00:00:28.871 --> 00:00:31.124
Right now, we stopped one.

00:00:32.130 --> 00:00:35.028
Ladies and gentlemen, we're doing it; it's working.

00:00:35.028 --> 00:00:39.788
Of course it's working—the power and the authority of the believer works—but there's fruit.

00:00:43.879 --> 00:00:46.800
There is fruit in what we're doing.

00:00:46.800 --> 00:01:09.810
There was a terrorist guy caught who had come across the border, and it was on all the news outlets.

00:01:09.810 --> 00:01:20.853
This guy lives two or three miles from my mom and dad's ranch.

00:01:20.853 --> 00:01:29.509
I told you they work for a guy raising Longhorn cattle.

00:01:29.509 --> 00:01:41.760
It's awesome because this guy had all kinds of plans.

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:56.700
My brother is part of the sheriff's department, on the SWAT team, and works with law enforcement.

00:01:56.700 --> 00:02:13.937
His boss told him, "We're on high alert from the FBI," and they're warning people to pray.

00:02:13.937 --> 00:02:29.267
My brother was telling me, "You need to be praying; we're on high alert.

00:02:29.267 --> 00:03:13.839
" The government's put us on high alert, and they were expecting some other kinds of groups, which I can't get into all that because I don't want to get anybody in trouble, but there is other stuff still set in motion that we need to be praying over.

00:03:13.839 --> 00:03:36.413
One of the people that came across the border, who was part of the ISIS group, was stopped.

00:03:36.413 --> 00:03:57.411
He had plans to do something during the 7th or 8th, the anniversary of the Israeli attack.

00:03:57.411 --> 00:04:10.983
He had all kinds of AK-47s and everything; he was ready to do something.

00:04:10.983 --> 00:04:37.733
I don't know if it was a group of guys or whatever, but all I want to tell you all is that prayer changes things.

00:04:37.733 --> 00:04:46.825
We have power and authority as believers to pray and bind things up.

00:04:52.462 --> 00:05:03.479
We don't have to have that going on in our neighborhoods, in our churches, or our community.

00:05:03.479 --> 00:05:25.404
Jesus came and gave us power and authority to tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:05:31.427 --> 00:05:39.215
I just want to encourage you all today because we are making a difference.

00:05:39.215 --> 00:05:51.080
Our little prayer group here of 50,000 or 60,000 people—we're doing something.

00:05:51.080 --> 00:06:09.613
That's a huge coliseum full of people praying, and I just want to encourage you all today about it.

00:06:09.613 --> 00:06:17.994
Now, I thought we'd take communion together.

00:06:17.994 --> 00:06:56.160
I'll wait a little bit if you want to get your communion and pray with me, but I just want to enter into worship and thank the Lord for all that he's done and all he's going to do.

00:07:06.004 --> 00:07:06.227
I know the enemy is not done.

00:07:06.227 --> 00:07:17.880
There's more coming; there's more coming in the name of Jesus.

00:07:17.880 --> 00:07:28.170
There's more uncovering coming; there's more exposing coming.

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:48.349
And the Lord told me we're going to pray over Coachella again, this Trump rally that's coming on Saturday.

00:08:01.365 --> 00:08:01.702
We're going to pray over that.

00:08:03.173 --> 00:08:11.927
We're going to pray over the voting—no fraudulent behavior, all kinds of stuff.

00:08:11.927 --> 00:08:18.350
We're going to take authority over this hurricane.

00:08:18.350 --> 00:08:41.651
Some people say, "Oh, that's the hand of God; that's judgment," but I don't believe God is bringing weather to judge Florida.

00:08:41.651 --> 00:09:13.570
If you believe that, that's on you, but the Bible says that the thief comes to kill, steal, and destroy, but God has come that we might have life and life more abundantly.

00:09:13.570 --> 00:09:22.187
He's not out there killing, stealing, and destroying—that's the devil's job.

00:09:34.125 --> 00:09:34.470
The devil and God are not buddying up.

00:09:34.470 --> 00:10:03.217
God is a good God, and he is faithful and able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:10:03.217 --> 00:10:11.040
Let's get on God's side about things.

00:10:11.040 --> 00:10:18.240
This is the God of the New Testament.

00:10:26.555 --> 00:10:26.910
God is a God of mercy and love.

00:10:26.910 --> 00:10:54.320
Yes, there's a shaking to awaken, and yes, we open the doors for the enemy to do things because we open the doors to sin.

00:10:54.320 --> 00:11:17.076
Seedtime and harvest are accelerating, and it's not God doing it; it's immoral behavior that opens the door and says, "Come on, Mr.

00:11:17.076 --> 00:11:20.536
Devil, come in here and mess with me.

00:11:20.536 --> 00:11:27.253
" God wants to show mercy; that's why he's saying pray.

00:11:27.253 --> 00:11:51.668
If he didn't want us to stop this, why would he want you to pray and then allow it to happen?

00:11:51.668 --> 00:11:54.000
That's boneheaded.

00:11:54.000 --> 00:12:03.000
God says, "I want you to stop this stuff.

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:12.159
I'm bringing you on here to change things.

00:12:12.159 --> 00:12:29.140
" I just want to encourage you all to get on the right side of things.

00:12:29.140 --> 00:12:50.720
We believe that God is a God of restoration and wanting to fix things.

00:12:50.720 --> 00:13:06.700
Like I said, whatever the devil means for bad, God is going to turn around for good.

00:13:06.700 --> 00:13:13.972
If something bad does happen in the natural, we'll pray good out of it.

00:13:13.972 --> 00:13:28.031
Let's pray that God turns it for good.

00:13:34.360 --> 00:13:49.840
The devil is an idiot, but I told you things were going to accelerate—the birthing pains, the labor pains.

00:13:59.941 --> 00:14:36.720
I told you when we passed Rosh Hashanah—I hope I didn't butcher that—the Lord said it would be a time of great acceleration with the weather, signs in the heavens, earthquakes, and wars and rumors of wars.

00:14:37.155 --> 00:14:55.422
The Lord said, "Brandon, it's going to increase by three times now.

00:14:55.422 --> 00:15:05.920
" And look at what's happening; it's increasing and increasing.

00:15:05.920 --> 00:15:39.777
It's going to keep getting that way all through this next year, but glory to God, the light is going to get lighter and the dark will get darker.

00:15:42.611 --> 00:15:51.928
We aren't focused on the dark; we're focused on the light.

00:15:51.928 --> 00:15:55.550
We're focused on Jesus.

00:15:56.640 --> 00:16:23.248
Father, I'm going to enter into your throne by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of my testimony.

00:16:44.332 --> 00:16:50.444
I thank you for your body that was broken for me.

00:16:50.444 --> 00:17:17.109
You were wounded for my transgressions and bruised for my iniquities; the chastisement of our peace was upon him, and with his stripes, we are healed.

00:17:17.109 --> 00:17:33.520
Christ has redeemed me from the curse of the law.

00:17:33.520 --> 00:18:14.702
He cast the spirits out with his word, healing all of their sicknesses, that it might be fulfilled which was spoken by the prophet: he himself took our infirmities and bore our sicknesses.

00:18:14.702 --> 00:18:35.267
He took it on his body, and this is his body, and he made a covenant.

00:18:35.267 --> 00:18:46.000
He was broken for us.

00:18:46.000 --> 00:19:26.866
So we take this communion right now in the name of Jesus and we say, "Father, I thank you for your body," and this is the meal that heals.

00:19:26.866 --> 00:20:04.987
When this goes in you, I take it by faith that there is no disease, no depression, no anxiety, no fear, no worries—nothing can be on me because I'm covered by his body and his blood.

00:20:04.987 --> 00:20:29.553
Now Lord, we take this blood and we apply the blood of Jesus over all our circumstances.

00:20:40.140 --> 00:20:48.600
This cup represents his blood, and it washes us from all our sins and all unrighteousness.

00:20:51.155 --> 00:20:58.880
We apply the blood over our house and our children.

00:20:58.880 --> 00:21:13.900
It makes us white as snow so I can come boldly before your throne.

00:21:19.770 --> 00:21:38.629
I take daily communion and I say, "Father, I come before your throne boldly," and he says, "Welcome back, Brandon.

00:21:38.629 --> 00:21:41.594
It's good to see you.

00:21:41.594 --> 00:21:46.880
" He loves on me.

00:21:46.880 --> 00:22:10.423
So Father, we take this blood and we apply it to our lives so that no weapon formed against us would prosper.

00:22:10.423 --> 00:22:18.700
Now we just give him praise.

00:22:18.700 --> 00:22:44.200
Thank you, Lord, that we enter into your throne by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony.

00:22:44.200 --> 00:22:54.475
Thank you, Jesus, that I'm healed and you set me free.

00:22:54.475 --> 00:23:33.236
Abraham staggered not at the promise of God through unbelief but was strong in faith, giving glory to God, fully persuaded that what God had promised he was able also to perform.

00:23:33.236 --> 00:23:43.679
It's time for overflow, ladies and gentlemen.

00:23:43.679 --> 00:24:11.707
We're going to believe God that more terrorists are exposed, that there is a covering, and that there are no mass shootings.

00:24:11.707 --> 00:24:25.280
I've told you we're going to pray over Coachella right now.

00:24:25.280 --> 00:24:29.669
So Father, in the name of Jesus, we come boldly before you.

00:24:40.004 --> 00:24:52.986
You warn me so that we would take our authority and say, "Satan, thus far and no further.

00:24:55.459 --> 00:25:18.533
" You will not do anything concerning Coachella or President Trump, or any harm or calamity that would come nigh any of them.

00:25:18.533 --> 00:25:37.140
We bind the maneuvering of the devil that is inside of these men or women.

00:25:37.140 --> 00:25:48.660
We sitting with you in the heavenlies, far above all principalities.

00:26:06.515 --> 00:26:15.440
We take our authority in this earth, and we thank you that these wicked events will not take place.

00:26:16.903 --> 00:28:05.597
We call supernatural wisdom over the Secret Service, the FBI, CIA, and Homeland Security.

00:28:05.597 --> 00:29:13.336
We pray a supernatural wisdom over the border agencies that there would be an uncovering of darkness.

00:29:13.336 --> 00:29:33.132
As for me and my house, we will be protected.

00:29:33.132 --> 00:29:53.079
We'll always be in the right place at the right time.

00:29:53.079 --> 00:30:32.110
We will not have any kind of demonic casualties, no fires, no tornadoes, no storms.

00:30:32.110 --> 00:30:45.880
No plagues or pestilence will come nigh us.

00:30:49.229 --> 00:30:59.209
We plead the blood of Jesus Christ over us.

00:30:59.209 --> 00:31:13.864
Father, I pray over the Yankees game and over the New York stadium.

00:31:13.864 --> 00:31:33.060
I've seen things in the spirit, and we take our authority over terrorist attacks concerning baseball games.

00:31:38.859 --> 00:31:54.648
The Lord pointed out to me, "Watch, pay attention to New York City and the Yankees.

00:31:54.648 --> 00:33:55.840
" I'm just going to tell you this: pray protection over the people participating in those games, that the audience will be protected from any drone things or any kind of calamity.

00:33:55.840 --> 00:34:57.100
Father, I thank you that there is no calamity that comes to these games.

