00:35:50.589 --> 00:36:02.200
Now God, I pray over our elections.

00:36:02.200 --> 00:37:16.839
I thank you that all hidden things be revealed and that it will be a fair, free election without corruption.

00:37:16.839 --> 00:39:10.839
Send your angelic visitation right now in the natural, like you did with Lot and Abraham when you sent the angels in physical form.

00:40:07.457 --> 00:40:07.880
I thank you that you would bring in angels of great protection.

00:40:22.149 --> 00:40:22.646
Whatever the devil meant for bad, you're going to expose it.

00:40:35.537 --> 00:40:41.670
We pray a hedge around the prayer conference for Billye Brim next week.

00:40:43.891 --> 00:40:56.960
We plead the blood of Jesus over the speakers and the attendees.

00:40:56.960 --> 00:41:19.857
We will have a glorious outpouring of the spirit of God like we have never seen before.

00:41:19.857 --> 00:41:52.689
Father, I thank you that this would be the time when the Shekinah glory cloud shows up and manifests in a way that we've not seen in this generation since Azusa Street.

00:41:52.689 --> 00:42:31.273
There will be a great demonstration of your glory, and all will be healed by the presence and power of God.

00:42:33.239 --> 00:42:44.315
