00:44:07.440 --> 00:44:19.023
Anoint our minds and hearts to think like you.

00:44:19.023 --> 00:44:29.140
We serve a God that is still the same today.

00:44:42.394 --> 00:44:47.999
We will be anointed with Holy Ghost and fire and speak with boldness.

00:44:47.999 --> 00:45:08.329
