00:45:56.104 --> 00:46:00.310
Breathe upon me, Breath of God.

00:46:00.310 --> 00:46:14.809
Holy, holy, holy is the Lord of hosts, who was and is and is to come.

00:46:14.809 --> 00:46:18.079
I exalt thee, oh Lord.

00:46:18.079 --> 00:46:26.796
Thank you for your mercy and your faithfulness.

00:46:33.983 --> 00:46:52.025
Whatever you need right now, hear the spirit of the Lord: be healed in the name of Jesus from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

00:46:52.025 --> 00:47:02.809
I call you healed and whole and well from everything that ails you.

00:47:11.827 --> 00:47:19.620
I stand in agreement with you that by his stripes you are healed.

00:47:25.853 --> 00:47:26.124
