01:09:16.589 --> 01:09:29.566
We're never going to be caught off guard.

01:09:31.520 --> 01:09:39.365
Lord, we worship you.

01:09:39.365 --> 01:09:56.692
You are more beautiful than diamonds and more precious than silver.

01:09:56.692 --> 01:10:05.813
I trust you, Lord.

01:10:05.813 --> 01:10:17.600
Meeting my needs today—I'm not going to worry.

01:10:17.600 --> 01:10:28.994
Oh, what a faithful God; you'll never let me down.

01:10:28.994 --> 01:11:54.229
