01:15:11.343 --> 01:15:33.106
North Korea, we thank you for bringing fire over North Korea and removing evil dictators.

01:15:33.106 --> 01:15:55.135
Your gospel will be preached throughout all the world, and then the end will come.

01:15:55.135 --> 01:16:12.760
