01:16:40.590 --> 01:16:46.669
People will see the glory on our faces and ask, 'What is this?

01:16:46.669 --> 01:17:21.784
' You will walk in the glory and demonstrations of my presence like you've never seen before.

01:18:07.017 --> 01:18:07.395
